{"tid":2326013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"消委會︱big big shop網購差 17訂單僅4張準時 送貨日失蹤累客呆等7小時拒退款","createTime":"2020-12-15T04:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-15T04:28:35.000Z","uid":48083,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8a467eba89f6fcede224e55b6fd6c02a0140cbcf","tid":2326013,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:11:17.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎疫情反覆，市民足不出戶，轉而網上超市購物。消委會實試5間網上超市的服務，分別包括「HKTVmall」、「惠康」、「百佳」、「city&rsquo;super」及「big big shop」。實測中數間超市的送貨服務皆出現混亂情況，如「big big shop」在5次實測中分17張訂單送貨，僅4張訂單準時送貨，更有實試員在指定送貨時間内在家中呆等約7小時，最後貨品失蹤，致電客服退訂，則被推説審批需時，結果在翌日貨品忽然送到，無視客戶的退訂要求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/PNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FPNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGNVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=d416b6ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201215%2FPNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU%2F&h=03b52651\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201215/PNHKCYZMWJDQBCP6QNKG7VUNZU/</a>"},{"pid":"0fb001f5027f0242f149f54fdabdc8a3dec2e28a","tid":2326013,"uid":201604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:11:55.000Z","msg":"抵啦 幫襯tvb"},{"pid":"7f51b22cb6242baa9e56a8bf290ec5d5ebfcc81e","tid":2326013,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f06f3fea7e8dd7a37fe9f685933f1427f691671","tid":2326013,"uid":158411,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"CCTVB會唔會報呢單新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef477b55a8743953756c2c2ad83de6640bebb93a","tid":2326013,"uid":53612,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"一話取消即刻送來<img src=\"/ass